```plantuml
@startuml gdsc-ys_mlops
left to right direction
skinparam rectangle {
  BackgroundColor #ffffff
  BorderColor black
  Style roundrect
}
skinparam defaultTextAlignment center

actor "ML Developer" as MLDev

rectangle "Client-Side Tools" as ClientTools {
  rectangle "MLflow Client" as MLflowClient
}

rectangle "Server Infrastructure" {
  rectangle "Nginx Reverse Proxy" as Nginx
  rectangle "MLflow Tracking Server" as MLflowServer
  database "MySQL Database" as MySQLDB
  rectangle "AWS S3" as S3
}

MLDev --> MLflowClient : Track Experiments\nLog Artifacts
MLflowClient --> Nginx : HTTP Requests
Nginx --> MLflowServer : Forward Requests
MLflowServer --> MySQLDB : Store Metadata
MLflowServer --> S3 : Store Artifacts

@enduml
```